{"tid":439872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廈門衛視「任性」不播十九大 傳將遭整頓改組","createTime":"2017-10-18T08:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T16:18:33.000Z","uid":76115,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"7d494e56306f3cf647613f7b4365da84fff81637","tid":439872,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:20:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.dwnews.com/china/big5/news/2017-10-18/60018059.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.dwnews.com%2Fchina%2Fbig5%2Fnews%2F2017-10-18%2F60018059.html&d=3l%2FqZyfP6LRDkR2YTTFA00%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=437001ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.dwnews.com/china/big5/news/2017-10-18/60018059.html</a><br />\n<br />\n即將開始第二任期的中國最高領導人習近平，在中共十九大上所作報告長達三個多小時。該報告將成為中國未來數十年發展方向和原則的規劃指導。中國官方媒體特別是電視頻道集中予以直播或轉播。<br />\n<br />\n不過網絡中傳出的一張多省主要官方電視台的轉播畫面中，只有廈門衛視沒有播放習近平在十九大作報道，頗顯突兀。不久即有消息稱，&ldquo;廈門衛視接到整改通知了&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic0.dwnews.net/20171018/772fc04805506244cc0cdfb9e7f2f95a_w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic0.dwnews.net%2F20171018%2F772fc04805506244cc0cdfb9e7f2f95a_w.png&h=9439e38f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廈門衛視未轉播中共十九大，成為輿論場中一個焦點（多維新聞制作）<br />\n<br />\n北京時間2017年10月18日上午9時，習近平開始作報告，直到中午12時30分左右才告結束。網絡中傳出的圖片顯示，浙江衛視、湖南衛視、江蘇衛視、深圳衛視等30餘家衛視都在轉播習近平作十九大報告，只有廈門衛視在播放一部名為&ldquo;鄭和下西洋&rdquo;的動畫片。<br />\n<br />\n在習近平作報告的三個多小時內，該衛視還播放了其他一些節目。<br />\n<br />\n一些網友稱該衛視&ldquo;任性&rdquo;、&ldquo;異端&rdquo;，有網友對該衛視可能遭到上級壓力表示擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n也有消息稱，&ldquo;據說廈門衛視和台灣東森（電視台）簽訂了落地，所以規定兩台都不播任何政治內容&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n不久，網絡中又傳出消息稱，&ldquo;廈門衛視接到整改通知了&rdquo;。同時流出的畫面顯示，廈門衛視畫面出現了&ldquo;xmtv頻道故障&rdquo;的字樣。"},{"pid":"25b4b40ee42e17427b325b4c4a30839b29480890","tid":439872,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"安心上路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4083d55510b73e2f2ecf48c752e57d172081616b","tid":439872,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勇者，安心上路"},{"pid":"119c46eb8192f9758d940cef2441fc86e4e30946","tid":439872,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"從此地球上消失了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7064004c32661b43db6d379a8ad9406dcee86e1","tid":439872,"uid":53687,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:57:19.000Z","msg":"黨大於合約，<br />\n依法治國喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5300c14fa0dc2c152a7eb745a17e5a5f726adacb","tid":439872,"uid":47359,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">站務台投訴三色貓</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/430728/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/430728/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"e0262210294772e781f20af286436d59574b2744","tid":439872,"uid":37735,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黨大於合約，<br />\n依法治國喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n班友打飛機<br />\n<br />\n雜畜守法<br />\n李剛咪又係叫佢老婆搭路雜畜老婆而無事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9f998fa8abfca2546503ec040dbf64cf0d6786","tid":439872,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黨大於合約，<br />\n依法治國喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n任何合約都有解除機制，只係錢的問題嚟。"},{"pid":"a4d03fb4553412a8da96e2a2889751235f582a17","tid":43